<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <title>구글 캘린더 연동 성공</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4 0%, #34a853 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      max-width: 500px;
      width: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .success-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4 0%, #34a853 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 40px 40px;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .success-header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 100 100"><defs><pattern id="dots" width="20" height="20" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"><circle cx="10" cy="10" r="1.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23dots)"/></svg>');
    }
    
    .success-icon {
      font-size: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
      40% {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }
      60% {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
      }
    }
    
    .success-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .success-subtitle {
      font-size: 16px;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 40px;
    }
    
    .message {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .features {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .features h3 {
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .feature-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }
    
    .feature-item:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    
    .feature-icon {
      margin-right: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .actions {
      margin-top: 32px;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 8px;
      min-width: 200px;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4285f4 0%, #34a853 100%);
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
      background: #6c757d;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #5a6268;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    
    .footer-text {
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
    }
    
    .confetti {
      position: fixed;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      background: #f39c12;
      animation: fall 3s linear infinite;
    }
    
    .confetti:nth-child(odd) {
      background: #e74c3c;
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      animation-duration: 2.5s;
    }
    
    .confetti:nth-child(even) {
      animation-duration: 3.5s;
    }
    
    @keyframes fall {
      to {
        transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg);
      }
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
      }
      
      .success-header {
        padding: 40px 20px 30px;
      }
      
      .success-icon {
        font-size: 60px;
      }
      
      .success-title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .btn {
        min-width: auto;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 8px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="success-header">
      <div class="success-icon">🎉</div>
      <h1 class="success-title">연동 성공!</h1>
      <p class="success-subtitle">구글 캘린더와 성공적으로 연결되었습니다</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p class="message">
        이제 연차가 승인되면 자동으로 구글 캘린더에<br>
        이벤트가 생성됩니다! 🗓️
      </p>
      
      <div class="features">
        <h3>✨ 앞으로 이런 기능들을 사용할 수 있어요</h3>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">🎯</span>
          <span>연차 승인 시 자동으로 캘린더 이벤트 생성</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">📅</span>
          <span>종일 이벤트로 생성되어 명확한 휴가 표시</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">🏷️</span>
          <span>연차 유형, 사유 등 상세 정보 포함</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <span class="feature-icon">🎨</span>
          <span>휴가 전용 색상으로 구분하여 표시</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="slack://open" class="btn btn-primary">
          💬 슬랙으로 돌아가기
        </a>
        <a href="/calendar-status?token=<%= token %>" class="btn btn-secondary">
          ⚙️ 연동 관리
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <p class="footer-text">
        구글 캘린더 연동을 언제든지 해제할 수 있습니다
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script>
    // 축하 애니메이션
    function createConfetti() {
      for (let i = 0; i < 50; i++) {
        setTimeout(() => {
          const confetti = document.createElement('div');
          confetti.className = 'confetti';
          confetti.style.left = Math.random() * 100 + 'vw';
          confetti.style.animationDelay = Math.random() * 3 + 's';
          confetti.style.backgroundColor = ['#e74c3c', '#f39c12', '#2ecc71', '#3498db', '#9b59b6'][Math.floor(Math.random() * 5)];
          document.body.appendChild(confetti);
          
          setTimeout(() => {
            confetti.remove();
          }, 4000);
        }, i * 50);
      }
    }
    
    // 페이지 로드 시 애니메이션
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
      const container = document.querySelector('.container');
      container.style.opacity = '0';
      container.style.transform = 'scale(0.9) translateY(20px)';
      
      setTimeout(() => {
        container.style.transition = 'all 0.6s ease';
        container.style.opacity = '1';
        container.style.transform = 'scale(1) translateY(0)';
      }, 100);
      
      // 축하 효과
      setTimeout(createConfetti, 500);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html> 